'''布魯斯·查德威克·雨果'''（{{lang-en|Bruce Chadwick Hugo}}；{{bd|1945年|9月11日|2017年|1月4日|catIdx=Hugo}}<ref name="Obituary">{{Cite web |url=http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/kansascity/obituary.aspx?n=william-j-cason&pid=183433926&fhid=21305 |title=William J. Cason's obituary |accessdate=2017-02-12 |archive-date=2017-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110090419/http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/kansascity/obituary.aspx?n=william-j-cason&pid=183433926&fhid=21305 |dead-url=no }}</ref>），是美國的[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]政治人物，前[[俄勒冈州众议院|俄勒冈州众议院]]議員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://library.state.or.us/repository/2011/201101131436324/index.pdf|title=Alphabetical List of Oregon Legislators and Related Information|accessdate=June 8, 2015|format=PDF|publisher=State of Oregon Legislative Administration Committee|year=1993|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304004154/http://library.state.or.us/repository/2011/201101131436324/index.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是一名通信顧問<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=DLqOAAAAMAAJ&q=%22HANLON,+TOM+D%E2%80%94+Dist.+2+b.+Hempstead,+NY+8/1945+1983/1985/1987***&dq=%22HANLON,+TOM+D%E2%80%94+Dist.+2+b.+Hempstead,+NY+8/1945+1983/1985/1987***&hl=en&sa=X&ei=dsg6VKayHYWpogTsooGoCA&ved=0CB4Q6AEwAA|title=Oregon Blue Book|publisher=Oregon Secretary of State|year=1987|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022085729/http://books.google.ca/books?id=DLqOAAAAMAAJ&q=%22HANLON%2C+TOM+D%E2%80%94+Dist.+2+b.+Hempstead%2C+NY+8%2F1945+1983%2F1985%2F1987%2A%2A%2A&dq=%22HANLON%2C+TOM+D%E2%80%94+Dist.+2+b.+Hempstead%2C+NY+8%2F1945+1983%2F1985%2F1987%2A%2A%2A&hl=en&sa=X&ei=dsg6VKayHYWpogTsooGoCA&ved=0CB4Q6AEwAA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==生平==
雨果於[[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]][[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特蘭]]出生，1983年起以[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]黨籍當選為俄勒冈州众议院第一選區代表議員，直到1993年卸任。2017年1月4日，雨果逝世<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pamplinmedia.com/obit/180-scs-obituaries/340199-220348-bruce-c-hugo|title=Bruce C. Hugo|author=Thill, Nicole|publisher=[[Pamplin_Media_Group|Pamplin Media Group]]|date=January 13, 2017|accessdate=January 24, 2017|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202034537/http://pamplinmedia.com/obit/180-scs-obituaries/340199-220348-bruce-c-hugo|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

